40:41.439 --> 40:43.316
What do you call this?

40:43.775 --> 40:45.448
How the heck did you do that?

40:45.610 --> 40:47.704
Oh, those must have been females!

40:49.322 --> 40:50.790
They look like males from down here.

40:51.282 --> 40:52.704
Females do sting.

40:52.867 --> 40:54.744
Just put some honey on those.

40:55.161 --> 40:57.209
- Honey? Really?
- Yeah.

40:57.705 --> 40:59.457
You put it on, you lick it off.
You feel much better.

40:59.958 --> 41:01.676
It's nature's ointment.

41:01.834 --> 41:03.381
I put it everywhere.

41:07.173 --> 41:08.174
Thanks.

41:08.341 --> 41:09.558
Okay, so, we're even now!

41:10.051 --> 41:11.177
Hold on a minute.

41:11.719 --> 41:12.811
What's your name anyway?

41:12.887 --> 41:14.810
We were never properly introduced.

41:14.973 --> 41:16.896
- Mowgli.
- Mowgli?

41:17.058 --> 41:20.528
Mowgli is a terrific name.

41:20.687 --> 41:23.236
I bet you got that one
all to yourself, too.

41:23.898 --> 41:24.899
Hey!

41:25.066 --> 41:26.409
Mowgli, look...

41:26.567 --> 41:29.070
I got a lot of gathering to do
these next couple of weeks...

41:29.612 --> 41:31.660
on account of the hibernation.

41:31.823 --> 41:33.621
I could really use your help.

41:33.783 --> 41:35.080
You know, if you stuck around...

41:35.243 --> 41:37.621
I can't. I have to go to the man village.

41:38.329 --> 41:39.501
Uh...

41:39.580 --> 41:41.127
For what reason, man village?

41:41.290 --> 41:43.463
I don't have a choice.
There's a tiger hunting me.

41:43.626 --> 41:45.253
Really? Why a tiger?

41:45.420 --> 41:46.922
Because I'm a man-cub, all right?

41:47.005 --> 41:48.427
Just leave me alone.

41:51.009 --> 41:54.434
Hey! Mowgli, my friend, my buddy, my pal.

41:54.595 --> 41:56.142
Slow down a second, handsome.

41:56.305 --> 41:58.478
Bagheera said I have to go
to the man village.

41:58.683 --> 42:02.779
Oh, Bagheera! I know him. Sure.

42:02.937 --> 42:04.530
You know what his problem is?

42:04.689 --> 42:06.862
He always plays by the rules.

42:07.025 --> 42:08.993
And, sometimes rules were meant to be...

42:09.152 --> 42:11.496
well, not necessarily broken,
but certainly bent.

42:11.654 --> 42:14.032
And definitely reinterpreted.
Don't you think?

42:14.198 --> 42:16.792
He told me to go to the man village,
so, that's where I'm gonna go!

42:16.868 --> 42:17.915
Okay, fine.

42:17.994 --> 42:19.621
You wanna go to the man village,
have it your way.

42:19.787 --> 42:21.630
In fact, I'll do you one better.

42:21.789 --> 42:23.666
I'll take you there myself.

42:23.833 --> 42:25.676
Come on, let's go. It's getting late.

42:30.798 --> 42:33.096
Bare necessities

42:33.176 --> 42:34.177
Forget about

42:34.635 --> 42:38.185
Your worries and your strife

42:38.347 --> 42:41.851
I mean the bare necessities

42:42.018 --> 42:43.361
What's that?

42:43.519 --> 42:45.817
That's a song about the good life.

42:46.606 --> 42:48.074
What's a song?

42:48.232 --> 42:50.906
You never heard a song before?

42:51.069 --> 42:52.946
Everyone's got a song.

42:53.112 --> 42:54.739
Didn't the wolves ever sing?

42:54.906 --> 42:56.123
I don't know.

42:56.240 --> 42:57.617
Uh... Oh...

42:58.284 --> 43:00.332
We recited the Law of the Jungle.

43:01.037 --> 43:03.005
"This is the Law of the Jungle...

43:03.164 --> 43:05.508
"as old and as true as the sky.

43:05.666 --> 43:07.509
"The Wolf that keeps it may prosper...

43:07.668 --> 43:10.387
"but the Wolf that breaks it will die."

43:11.714 --> 43:13.842
Kid, that's not a song.

43:14.008 --> 43:15.931
That's propaganda.

43:18.846 --> 43:20.769
What's propaganda?

43:27.396 --> 43:28.739
Just a little farther.

43:37.031 --> 43:38.783
That's the man village?

43:38.950 --> 43:41.624
Yep. You can always
tell by the Red Flower.

43:42.161 --> 43:44.038
They do love their Red Flower.

43:46.582 --> 43:49.131
The Red Flower doesn't seem so bad.

43:49.293 --> 43:50.294
Yeah.

43:50.378 --> 43:53.348
Let it loose, and it destroys
everything it touches.

43:53.506 --> 43:54.507
Don't ever play with it.

43:54.924 --> 43:55.971
You got that?

43:56.050 --> 43:57.222
Yeah, I got it.

43:57.385 --> 43:58.386
Good.

44:04.183 --> 44:06.606
Do you think that's where I'm from?

44:07.103 --> 44:08.104
Could be.

44:08.229 --> 44:10.106
I don't know, kid. Does it look familiar?

44:10.565 --> 44:11.566
I don't remember it.

44:11.649 --> 44:14.744
All I remember is living with the wolves.

44:15.486 --> 44:17.534
Why do you wanna go there?

44:17.697 --> 44:19.699
Bagheera said I need a people.

44:20.449 --> 44:22.668
Again, with the listening to Bagheera.

44:22.827 --> 44:24.500
Hey, he's my friend, okay?

44:24.954 --> 44:27.207
Now I don't even know where he is.

44:31.878 --> 44:34.677
I can't believe I'm leaving
the Jungle for good.

44:34.839 --> 44:36.261
May I say just one thing?

44:36.883 --> 44:39.136
What I saw you do today,
I've never seen anything like it.

44:39.302 --> 44:41.350
I've been trying to get
that honey for years.

44:42.388 --> 44:43.981
But I used my tricks.

44:44.140 --> 44:45.357
What tricks?

44:46.267 --> 44:47.268
You know...

44:48.060 --> 44:50.859
Everything that I built.
It's not the wolf way.

44:51.314 --> 44:52.816
Who cares? "The wolf way."

44:52.982 --> 44:54.484
That's the Mowgli way.

44:54.650 --> 44:55.902
That's the Baloo way.

44:56.068 --> 44:57.194
That's our way.

44:57.361 --> 44:58.738
That's how we get things done.

44:58.905 --> 45:00.828
I can't even imagine what kind
of potential you'd have...

45:01.282 --> 45:03.159
if you had somebody like me
helping you out.

45:04.535 --> 45:06.663
You say you want to go to the man village.

45:07.163 --> 45:09.666
I say, you could be a man right here.

45:11.000 --> 45:12.001
I'll tell you what.

45:12.168 --> 45:13.841
Now you know where the man village is.

45:14.003 --> 45:16.347
You can always go down there,
whenever you want.

45:16.881 --> 45:20.264
But I would personally appreciate it
as a personal favour to me, personally...

45:20.426 --> 45:23.145
if we just worked together,
just us, tricks and all.

45:24.347 --> 45:26.475
I think it would be interesting to see...

45:26.641 --> 45:28.814
just how much honey we could accumulate...

45:29.227 --> 45:30.353
before winter.

45:30.519 --> 45:32.942
Whatever I could do to make
your trickiness happen...

45:33.105 --> 45:34.197
I will do.

45:34.357 --> 45:37.156
And if it turns out to
not be fun for you...

45:37.318 --> 45:40.288
I will walk you right down
to that man village myself.

45:40.404 --> 45:41.405
Is that a deal?

45:43.908 --> 45:45.660
Just till winter.

45:47.578 --> 45:49.080
Just till winter.

45:57.630 --> 45:59.348
Ami, wake up.

46:05.012 --> 46:06.514
Pups?

46:06.681 --> 46:08.308
They're up there.

46:15.147 --> 46:17.946
The deer, of course,
take comfort in numbers.

46:18.734 --> 46:22.079
They lack defences most animals will have.

46:22.238 --> 46:24.536
And if we're being honest...

46:24.699 --> 46:27.293
they're not very smart either.

46:27.451 --> 46:30.208
Unlike the mother crocodile,
who is a good deal more clever.

46:34.917 --> 46:37.716
But the one you have to watch out for...

46:37.878 --> 46:40.381
is the cuckoo bird.

46:40.840 --> 46:44.219
Do you know how the cuckoo bird survives?

46:45.136 --> 46:47.559
By preying on a mother's weakness.

46:47.722 --> 46:51.067
The cuckoo bird is too clever
to raise its young.

46:51.225 --> 46:52.351
Instead, it sneaks...

46:52.727 --> 46:55.480
its eggs into the nests of simpler birds.

46:55.646 --> 46:57.148
So, when they hatch...

46:57.315 --> 46:59.317
the mother bird is fooled.

46:59.483 --> 47:01.827
She feeds them, nurtures them.

47:02.820 --> 47:05.915
And do you know what happens
to her own chicks?

47:06.741 --> 47:08.288
They starve...

47:08.451 --> 47:09.668
and die...

47:09.827 --> 47:11.295
from neglect.

47:12.079 --> 47:14.958
All because a mother loved a chick...

47:16.834 --> 47:18.836
that wasn't her own.

47:20.254 --> 47:21.847
Come now, time for sleep.

47:38.981 --> 47:40.983
I think they like me.

47:42.818 --> 47:44.536
Why are you doing this?

47:45.446 --> 47:46.493
He's gone.

47:46.655 --> 47:48.453
Isn't that what you wanted?

47:49.992 --> 47:51.494
I want him dead.

47:56.457 --> 47:58.676
Once he gets word of what happened here...

47:58.834 --> 48:00.211
he'll come back.

48:01.003 --> 48:03.131
And I'll be waiting.

