50:43.457 --> 50:45.551
Baloo, Baloo, Baloo... look.

50:49.672 --> 50:51.299
Stay low on my back.

50:59.223 --> 51:00.816
Come on out and show yourself.

51:08.524 --> 51:10.492
Bagheera! Ah!

51:11.068 --> 51:12.069
Mowgli.

51:13.028 --> 51:15.326
Oh, I was looking everywhere for you!

51:15.406 --> 51:16.658
