51:16.824 --> 51:18.326
- Are you all right?
- Yeah!

51:18.701 --> 51:20.920
I can't believe you found me!
I was so worried about you.

51:21.412 --> 51:23.665
I was lost, and I didn't know
what happened...

51:23.831 --> 51:25.083
but then I met Baloo.

51:25.249 --> 51:27.172
And then he saved me from a giant snake!

51:27.376 --> 51:28.923
And now we're working together!

51:29.420 --> 51:31.013
Really? That's a new wrinkle.

51:31.171 --> 51:32.639
